entry.title: $2400 // 2 bedroom apartment for Rent Woodside/Northern Blvd 4 mins to Subway
entry.content:
Newly Renovated Modern Apartment with everything Brand New!

It is a 2 bedroom Apartment with newly installed beautiful hardwood Oak floors. Open floor with Living and Kitchen. The Kitchen comes with NEW Cabinets, Counter tops and Stainless Steel Appliances. Kitchen Island can be used as dining table which can seat up to 5 people. Big windows in all rooms with natural light.
BEST of ALL easily accessible to Subway Station M, R only 4 mins walk.

25 mins to Manhattan by car and 30 mins subway.

Parking on site Available!! Inquire! Extra fee may apply
